或特區政府的憎恨。違反上述罪名，可被判處3年以上10年以下有期徒刑；罪行重大的，處無期徒刑或者10年以上有期徒刑。"},"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"「團伙」蝗語。一定出自支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:43:44.000Z","msg":"唸咁好撚耐係咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ff607eb6337d4407a5bd9300de148b9b7217ba","tid":2151231,"uid":221988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫團伙呀屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d8c73269e966e28afc3fc12d9294a0709b5f5e","tid":2151231,"uid":287981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"原來團火係團伙<br />\n明了<br />\n真係唔明點解用D咁令香港人唔明嘅用語"},{"pid":"e4a4cd6bd7c4aac130a05c1bcb3431e494bd1d0c","tid":2151231,"uid":71210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:47:19.000Z","msg":"一百萬夠Jimmy間屋交幾多個月租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n窮酸警甴係咪想笑死人"},{"pid":"86197294411a28367135bc2a5b1c77e854869174","tid":2151231,"uid":294502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"今日賣報紙收左好多現金添，不如查下資金來源呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a76867dfc807d31e8eddb00dc0e5ef8853362aa","tid":2151231,"uid":173844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>警方追查發現有一群傳媒機構高層透過多個本地及海外銀行戶口，將一筆款項轉入一個團伙</strong><br />\n<br />\n睇完都唔知講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又一群又多個 又變返一筆轉入一個<br />\n「團伙」咁大個人都未聽過"},{"pid":"a817f7c32ab4d94f19084bac8a6bd49be3e028a4","tid":2151231,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"即係以前孫中山做嘅事？"},{"pid":"cb41debe0404947cac12b8b4baffd8c1f343ea53","tid":2151231,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0